quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  11,61,Al Thamoud ni send their frat Saaleh. Li dir O my popol worship DI; vi ne hav ali di Him. Li iniciat vi ter tiam sald vi en gxi. Vi streb His forgiveness tiam pent Him. My Lord est cxiam proksim responsive
  11,62,Ili dir O Saaleh vi uz est popular among us this. Vi enjoining us el worshipping ki our parents worshipping Ni est plen de dub cxio vi told us
  11,63,Li dir O my popol ki mi hav solid proof el my Lord mercy Him? Who support me DI mi disobeyed Him? Vi nur eg my loss
  11,64,O my popol this est di kamel serv proof vi. Vi let her mangx di ter do ne tusx her any harm lest vi incur immediate retribution
  11,65,Ili bucx her. Li tiam dir Vi hav nur 3 tag viv This est prophecy est inevitable
  11,66,When our judgment ven ni sav Saaleh those kred him mercy us humiliation ke tag. Your Lord est plej Powerful Almighty
  11,67,Those transgressed annihilated disaster las them their hejm dead
  11,68,Est as se ili neniam viv tie. Ja Thamoud rejected their Lord Absolutely Thamoud incurred their annihilation